Package: max-ardesia
Architecture: all
Depends: ardesia, curtain, florence, magnifier, spotlighter
Recommends: easystroke
Description: Ardesia is a free digital sketchpad.
 You can make colored free-hand annotations with digital ink everywhere,
 record it and share on the network.
 .
 Thanks to Ardesia you are free to open any application
 and fix your ideas and comments as if you wrote on a classic chalkboard.
 You can use the tool to make effective on-screen presentation,
 highlight things or point out things of interest.
 The tool facilitates the online presentations and demos showing in real time
 your computer screen to anyone in the network.
 You can use this tool to enhance your lessons or courses working with
 your preferred applications and your preferred operating system.
 Create nice tutorial and demos saving the desktop images
 with your free hand annotations.
 Ardesia includes a sketchpad software that allow to free-hand draw
 geometrical shapes using the shape recognizer.
 .
 Ardesia works with all the pointing device; you can use a mouse,
 a touch screen, a drawing tablet, a cheap&professional wiimote whiteboard
 or a commercial whiteboard, interactive projector and
 any other devices supported by your operating system.


Package: ardesia
Depends: binutils, vlc, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: max-ardesia (<< 0.8)
Architecture: any
Description: The free digital sketchpad.
 You can make colored free-hand annotations with digital ink everywhere,
 record it and share on the network.
 .
 Thanks to Ardesia you are free to open any application
 and fix your ideas and comments as if you wrote on a classic chalkboard.
 You can use the tool to make effective on-screen presentation,
 highlight things or point out things of interest.
 The tool facilitates the online presentations and demos showing in real time
 your computer screen to anyone in the network.
 You can use this tool to enhance your lessons or courses working with
 your preferred applications and your preferred operating system.
 Create nice tutorial and demos saving the desktop images
 with your free hand annotations.
 Ardesia includes a sketchpad software that allow to free-hand draw
 geometrical shapes using the shape recognizer.
 .
 Ardesia works with all the pointing device; you can use a mouse,
 a touch screen, a drawing tablet, a cheap&professional wiimote whiteboard
 or a commercial whiteboard, interactive projector and
 any other devices supported by your operating system.

Package: curtain
Conflicts: max-ardesia (<< 0.8)
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Curtain on the screen.
 Curtain enables you to show, move and resizeresize a curtain on the desktop.
 .
 This is especially useful when making presentations to hide and unhide things.
 .
 Curtain is XInput-Aware, so you can use it with a graphic tablet or a whiteboard.

Package: florence
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: max-ardesia (<< 0.8)
Description: Virtual keyboard.
 Florence-ramble is a florence virtual keyboard flavour powered by the stroke taste.
 .
 This is especially useful as fast input text insertion device.
 .
 FlorenceRamble is XInput-Aware, so you can use this with a graphic tablet or a whiteboard.

Package: magnifier
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: max-ardesia (<< 0.8)
Description: Virtual Magnifier Glass.
 Virtual Magnifier Glass magnify your desktop.
 .
 This is especially useful when making presentations to highlight things.
 .
 Vmg is XInput-Aware, so you can use it with a graphic tablet or a whiteboard.

Package: spotlighter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: max-ardesia (<< 0.8)
Description: Gtk interface to make annotations on the screen.
 Spotlighter enables you to show, move and resize a spotlight on the desktop.
 .
 This is especially useful when making presentations, to highlight point of interest.
 .
 Curtain is XInput-Aware, so you can use it with a graphic tablet or a whiteboard.
